tty-healy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-1975-matty-healy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-1975-matty-healy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-1975-matty-healy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975 乐队</a>被责令在 7 天内向马来西亚音乐节组织者支付超过 200 万英镑的损失，否则将在英国面临法律诉讼。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-1975-at-lollapalooza-2023-lots-of-hits-and-a-little-bit-of-drama-3478624">2023 年 Lollapalooza 的 1975 年：大量热门歌曲和“一点戏剧性”</a></strong></li></ul><p>吉隆坡 Good Vibes 音乐节 (GVF) 的主办方 Future Sound Asia (FSA) 确认已向英国乐队发出为期 7 天的索赔信，要求在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healy-3471893">取消</a>后赔偿 1,230 万令吉（2,099,154.54 英镑）的损失<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healy-3471893">上个月的节日</a>。</p><p>索赔函此前已于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/good-vibes-festival-pursue-legal-action-over-matty-healy-the-1975-set-3479272">8 月 7 日公布，但当时尚不清楚更多细节</a>。</p><p>在给<a href="https://www.malaymail.com/news/showbiz/2023/08/08/the-1975-given-seven-days-to-pay-rm123m-in-damages-or-face-legal-suit-in-uk/84146" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《马来邮报》</em></a>的一份新声明中，音乐节组织者来自 Steven Thiru &amp; Sudhar Partnership 的法律顾问 David Mathew 表示，7 天的通知日期为 8 月 7 日，这意味着乐队必须在 8 月 14 日之前支付损害赔偿金，然后才能采取法律行动。反对他们。</p><p> David Mathew 告诉<em>《马来邮报</em>》：“在信中，FSA 要求 The 1975 承认自己的责任，并在七 (7) 天内支付 2,099,154.54 英镑（12,347,967.91 令吉）。” “索赔书是根据《英国实践指导诉前行为和协议》的规定撰写的，这些规定是英国民事诉讼规则的一部分。” </p><figure id="attachment_3471896" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3471896" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3471896" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg" alt="1975年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3471896" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 6 月，马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy) 与 The 1975 一起现场表演。图片来源：Thomas Niedermueller/Getty Images。</figcaption></figure><p>据马修称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/good-vibes-festival-pursue-legal-action-over-matty-healy-the-1975-set-3479272">FSA 索赔信的很大一部分归因于主唱马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy) 的违约行为</a>。马修斯对《<em>马来邮报》</em>表示：“希利的代表明确提供了演出前的书面保证，他和 The 1975 的现场表演在马来西亚演出期间‘将遵守所有当地准则和规定’。”</p><p> “尽管如此，这一保证却被忽视，乐队的行为也明显违反了与 FSA 的合同，导致音乐节取消，给 FSA 造成重大损失。”</p><p>乐队未能满足 FSA 的索赔书将导致在英国提起法律诉讼，但具体细节在发布时仍不清楚。</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系 The 1975 的代表征求意见。</p><p> FSA 的索赔信是在 7 月 21 日 The 1975 在 Good Vibes 音乐节第一天的马来西亚演出中被禁止之后发出的。在为期三天的音乐节第一天的头条表演中，乐队的 Matty Healy <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-good-vibes-festival-malaysia-set-cut-short-matty-healy-criticises-anti-lgbtq-laws-kiss-bassist-3471738">批评马来西亚政府反 LGBTQ 法律在吉隆坡 Good Vibes Festival 上成为头条新闻</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3478629" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3478629" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3478629" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-again-Barry-BrecheisenWireImage.jpg" alt="1975年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-again-Barry-BrecheisenWireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-again-Barry-BrecheisenWireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-again-Barry-BrecheisenWireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-again-Barry-BrecheisenWireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-again-Barry-BrecheisenWireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-again-Barry-BrecheisenWireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3478629" class="wp-caption-text"> 1975 年图片来源：Barry Brecheisen</figcaption></figure><p> “我犯了一个错误。当我们预订演出时，我没有考虑这一点。我不明白邀请 1975 到一个国家然后告诉我们可以和谁发生性关系有什么意义，”希利说。</p><p>他继续说道：“如果这冒犯了你，我很抱歉，你是有宗教信仰的，这是你他妈的政府的一部分，但你的政府是一群他妈的白痴，我不在乎了。如果你推，我就会反击。我他妈没有心情，我他妈没有心情。”</p><p>希利<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-good-vibes-festival-malaysia-set-cut-short-matty-healy-criticises-anti-lgbtq-laws-kiss-bassist-3471738">随后在舞台上亲吻了乐队成员兼贝斯手罗斯·麦克唐纳 (Ross MacDonald) 的</a>嘴唇，之后他们的演出被缩短了两首歌——他们的演出名单中只有七首歌——并且宣布乐队被禁止进入马来西亚并不得不离开。第二天，马来西亚政府<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healy-3471893">下令取消剩余两天的好氛围节</a>。</p><p>继上个月登上头条新闻后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/malaysian-lgbtq-community-condemn-the-1975s-matty-healy-over-kiss-incident-3472210">马来西亚 LGBTQ+ 群体谴责了希利</a>，并表示希利的行为将使该国 LGBTQ+ 群体的生活变得更糟。</p><p>最近，希利<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/matty-healy-1975-address-malaysia-controversy-good-vibes-festival-3479651">在夏威夷的一场音乐会上谈到了这一争议</a>。 “我要说的是，我才不在乎任何白人救世主情结的废话。我要说的是，做正确的事往往需要大量的牺牲和很少的回报。被看到做正确的事只需要很少的牺牲，那就是你获得所有回报的时候，”希利说。 “我和罗斯（麦克唐纳）差点剃光头，因为我们认为我们会因为混蛋而进监狱”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-pay-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-organiser-2million-face-legal-action-uk-3480908">《The 1975》在 7 天内向马来西亚音乐节组织者支付 200 万英镑，否则将在英国面临法律诉讼的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
乐队成员罗比·罗伯逊去世，享年 80 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-band-robbie-robertson-has-died-ged-80-3480702?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-band-robbie-robertson-has-died- 80岁Surej SinghThu, 10 Aug 2023 02:40:01 +0000 Music NewsNews.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3480702 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗比·罗伯逊" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>马丁·斯科塞斯、林戈·斯塔尔、乔尼·米切尔、尼尔·戴蒙德等人向这位已故音乐家致敬</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-band-robbie-robertson-has-died-aged-80-3480702">乐队成员 Robbie Robertson 去世，享年 80 岁的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗比·罗伯逊" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Robbie-Robertson-The-Band-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-band">乐队</a>吉他手兼创作型歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-robertson">罗比·罗伯逊</a>去世。他80岁了。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/the-bands-robbie-robertson-interview-once-were-brothers-2754474">乐队的罗比·罗伯逊（Robbie Robertson）：“如果说《最后的华尔兹》有什么问题的话，那就是可卡因不太好”</a></strong></li></ul><p>周三晚（8 月 9 日），乐队管理层在社交媒体上证实了这一消息。这份最初来自罗伯逊家人的声明写道：“罗比去世时，他的家人围绕在他身边，包括他的妻子珍妮特、前妻多米尼克、她的伴侣尼古拉斯以及他的孩子亚历山德拉、塞巴斯蒂安、德尔菲娜，还有德尔菲娜的搭档肯尼。”</p><p>罗比·罗伯逊身后留下了他的孙子安吉丽卡、多诺万、多米尼克、加布里埃尔和塞拉菲娜。</p><p>罗伯逊的家人呼吁向大河六国捐款，以代替送花。这些捐款将用于支持新的林地文化中心。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvvSwZBLy52/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-ru