加奈尔·梦奈 (Janelle Monae) 为“欢乐时代”北美巡演增加额外日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/janelle-monae-adds-extra-dates-to-age-of-pleasure-north-american-tour-3480650?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=janelle-monae-为欢乐时代北美巡演添加额外日期Emma WilkesWed, 09 Aug 2023 20:40:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3480650 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="加奈尔·梦奈" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艺术家在巡演中额外增加了八场演出</p><p>加奈尔·梦奈<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janelle-monae-adds-extra-dates-to-age-of-pleasure-north-american-tour-3480650">(Janelle Monae) 为“欢乐时代”北美巡演增加额外日期的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="加奈尔·梦奈" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/janelle-monae-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">加奈尔·梦奈 (Janelle Monae)</a>为即将到来的“欢乐时代”北美演出增加了许多额外的演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/janelle-monae-the-age-of-pleasure-review-3452703">加奈尔·梦奈 (Janelle Monáe) 的《快乐时代》评论：一次毫不掩饰性感的声音之旅</a></strong></li></ul><p>Monae 将在印第安纳州印第安纳波利斯和哥伦布以及新奥尔良和华盛顿特区进行额外的演出，加拿大温哥华也将举行一场演出。</p><p>在最近接受<em><a tabindex="0" href="https://apnews.com/article/janelle-monae-age-of-pleasure-interview-59fb1bcc01d0410902e09470d71ba8fc" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" data-t="{&quot;n&quot;:&quot;destination&quot;,&quot;t&quot;:13,&quot;b&quot;:1,&quot;c.t&quot;:7}">美联社新闻</a></em>采访时，莫奈解释了她认为她的歌迷应该如何为“欢乐时代”巡演做好准备。 “利用你的自由能量。这植根于自爱，而不是傲慢，”莫奈说。 “利用这个空间，然后互相照顾。这就是我所希望的。通过我所做的表演，当我向外看时，这是一种体验。就像我们自己的教堂一样。你们想互相照顾。</p><p> “即使你的自由看起来不像那个人的自由，你也会明白我们正在与比我们大得多的东西作斗争，”莫奈继续说道。 “我们正在系统性地与比我们大得多的东西作斗争，所以我们必须团结起来，我们必须团结在一起。我们必须确保我们彼此出现。如果我们在某些领域拥有特权，请确保我们伸出援手，发出声音，放大信息。”查看下面的附加日期的完整列表，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fjanelle-monae-tickets%2Fartist%2F1216463" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找门票。</p><p><strong>加奈尔·梦奈“Age Of Pleasure”新北美巡演日期为：</strong></p><p><strong>八月</strong><br /><strong>30 – 华盛顿州西雅图，WAMU 剧院</strong><br /><strong>31 – 温哥华，不列颠哥伦比亚省，UBC 道格·米切尔雷鸟体育中心</strong></p><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>2 – 俄勒冈州波特兰，RV Inn Style Resorts Amphitheatre</strong><br /> <strong>6 – 犹他州盐湖城综合楼</strong><br /><strong>7 – 科罗拉多州莫里森，红岩露天剧场</strong><br /><strong>9 – 密苏里州堪萨斯城，米德兰剧院</strong><br /><strong>10 – 印第安纳州印第安纳波利斯，老国家剧院的埃及厅</strong><br /><strong>11 - 明尼苏达州明尼阿波利斯，军械库</strong></p><figure id="attachment_3453256" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3453256" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3453256" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Janelle-Monae-1.jpg" alt="加奈尔·梦奈" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Janelle-Monae-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Janelle-Monae-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Janelle-Monae-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Janelle-Monae-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Janelle-Monae-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Janelle-Monae-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3453256" class="wp-caption-text">加奈尔·梦奈，2023（图片：媒体）</figcaption></figure><p> Monae 最近还分享了他们从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince 那里</a>学到的东西，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/theres-good-reason-janelle-monaes-huge-new-single-sounds-like-prince-2249246">之前曾与 Prince 合作过</a>。<br /> “把它切成两半。这就是普林斯会对他的乐队说的话，”他们透露。 “他会说，有时当人们感到紧张或紧张时，他们会弹得太快或者说得很快。他说，‘把一切都减半。’”</p><p> “我在生活中采取了这种方法，把生活减半，”莫奈补充道。 “有时候你必须说不。有时你会错过一些你认为可以让你更上一层楼的机会。因为它总是像，好吧，如果他们不再给我打电话怎么办？那种恐惧，你必须面对它。我必须处理它。我当时想，你知道吗？我必须意识到，在我身边就是我的北极星。”</p><p>加奈尔·梦奈<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janelle-monae-adds-extra-dates-to-age-of-pleasure-north-american-tour-3480650">(Janelle Monae) 为“欢乐时代”北美巡演增加额外日期的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
比利·波特表示，由于持续罢工，他不得不卖掉自己的房子https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-porter-says-he-has-to-sell-his-house-due-to-ongoing-strikes-3480654?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billy-波特说，由于持续的罢工，他必须卖掉他的房子Hollie GeraghtyWed, 09 Aug 2023 20:24:20 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3480654 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比利·波特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “艺术家的生活，直到你赚到他妈的钱——我还没赚到——仍然是支票到支票”</p><p>比利<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-porter-says-he-has-to-sell-his-house-due-to-ongoing-strikes-3480654">·波特 (Billy Porter) 表示，由于持续的罢工，他必须卖掉自己的房子。该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比利·波特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/billy-porter-house-strikes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-porter">比利·波特</a>表示，由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/strike-actors-writers-hollywood-when-will-it-end-3477098">好莱坞持续的罢工，</a>他将不得不卖掉自己的房子。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/strike-actors-writers-hollywood-when-will-it-end-3477098">好莱坞罢工！关于演员和作家抗议的每个问题都得到了解答</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位演员、歌手和舞台明星因电视连续剧<em>《Pose》、</em>卡米拉·卡贝洛 (Camila Cabello) 主演的 2021 年<em>灰姑娘</em>音乐电影以及他获得托尼奖的百老汇生涯而闻名。他表示，好莱坞持续的演员和编剧罢工造成了财务不确定性。</p><p>波特表示，他计划返回美国后“加入纠察队”，并在接受《 <em><a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/insider/billy-porter-interview-actor-writers-strike-strange-loop-b1098710.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">标准晚报》</a></em>采访时补充说，他对流媒体的缺陷和对生活工资的要求感到“愤怒”。 “我必须卖掉我的房子，”他说。 </p><figure id="attachment_2938540" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2938540" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2938540" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/billy_porter_nme_brit_awards_2000.jpg" alt="2021 年 5 月 11 日，比利·波特 (Billy Porter) 在英国伦敦 O2 体育馆举行的 2021 年全英音乐奖颁奖典礼期间在媒体室摆姿势。 （摄影：JMEnternational/JMEnternational for BRIT Awards/Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/billy_porter_nme_brit_awards_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/billy_porter_nme_brit_awards_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/billy_porter_nme_brit_awards_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/billy_porter_nme_brit_awards_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/billy_porter_nme_brit_awards_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/billy_porter_nme_brit_awards_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2938540" class="wp-caption-text"> 2021 年 5 月 11 日，比利·波特 (Billy Porter) 在英国伦敦 O2 体育馆举行的 2021 年全英音乐奖颁奖典礼期间在媒体室摆姿势。 （摄影：JMEnternational/JMEnternational for BRIT Awards/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> “我不知道我们什么时候才能回去工作，”波特在谈到演员罢工时补充道。 “艺术家的生活，直到你赚到了他妈的钱——我还没赚到——仍然是一张张支票。我原本应该出演一部新电影，以及九月份开始的一部新电视节目。这些都没有发生。</p><p> “所以，对于那些说‘我们要让他们挨饿直到他们不得不卖掉公寓’的人来说，”他补充道，并解释了一位不愿透露姓名的工作室高管的一句话（来自<em><a href="https://deadline.com/2023/07/writers-strike-hollywood-studios-deal-fight-wga-actors-1235434335/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deadline</a></em> ），“你已经让我挨饿了” ”。</p><p> The actor was being interviewed about his music career, with his new album &#39;The Black Mona Lisa&#39; scheduled for release later this year. </p><figure id="attachment_3477201" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477201" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3477201" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles.jpg" alt="罢工" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Hollywood_Strikes_Los_Angeles-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3477201" class="wp-caption-text"> CREDIT: Getty</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/famous-actors-striking-hollywood-picket-lines-sag-aftra-3469811">Dozens of famous faces have joined the picket lines</a> in support of the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/why-are-actors-striking-in-hollywood-3468340">Hollywood strikes</a> , including Bryan Cranston, Kevin Bacon, Susan Sarandon, Awkwafina, Paul Dano and Olivia Wilde.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">Will Smith</a> also recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-hollywood-actors-strike-pivotal-moment-for-our-profession-3476622">described the Hollywood strikes as a “pivotal moment”</a> in the industry, while <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dwayne-johnson-makes-historic-donation-to-hollywood-actors-strike-3472840">Dwayne Johnson made a “historic” donation to the actor&#39;s strike</a> .</p><p> Last month, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mark-ruffalo-criticises-hollywood-fat-cats-amid-actors-strike-3469562">Mark Ruffalo urged fellow actors and writers to work together to make independent projects</a> to cut out Hollywood&#39;s “fat cats”.</p><p> In the music industry, meanwhile, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-cancels-hollywood-bowl-shows-in-solidarity-with-writers-and-actors-strike-doggystyle-30th-anniversary-3473665">cancelled his Hollywood Bowl shows in Los Angeles in solidarity</a> with the strikes.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-porter-says-he-has-to-sell-his-house-due-to-ongoing-strikes-3480654">Billy Porter says he has to sell his house due to ongoing strikes</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
